# [SUIT](../wg/suit.html)

## Summary
The SUIT Working Group held an interim meeting on June 18, 2026. The session focused on the status and recent updates of three core WG documents: the SUIT Manifest (`draft-ietf-suit-manifest`), the SUIT Report (`draft-ietf-suit-report`), and SUIT Update Management (`draft-ietf-suit-update-management`). Key updates focused on aligning CDDL specifications with text descriptions, addressing IANA and directorate feedback, and fixing minor inconsistencies discovered through implementation experience. 

